<Annotations start="0">
  <!--
    HOW TO ADD A NEW SITE:
    1. Copy an <Annotation> block below
    2. Change the "about" URL pattern (what Google searches)
    3. Update "display_name" to the company name
    4. Update "href" to the direct careers page link
    5. Save this file and push to GitHub
    6. Upload to Google PSE: Setup → Sites to search → Advanced → Add annotations file

    NOTE: Replace "_cse_YOUR_ENGINE_ID" with your actual Search Engine ID
    after creating your Programmable Search Engine.
  -->

